data.description: Incredibly Beautiful custom home on 2.5 acres close to the Tonto Forest. This home offers Views in all directions from its numerous balconies! Top-of-the line custom finishes throughout w/gourmet kitchen, granite counters, stainless appliances, kitchen island opens into the great room. Full 3rd bedroom en-suite downstairs has a walk-in closet and perfect as an office, guest suite, 2nd master bedroom, with its own separate exit to the outside. Master suite and 2nd bedroom upstairs have wood flooring. Luxurious master has tub with jets, shower with pebble flooring, double vanities and balcony for enjoying the sunset. Second bedroom upstairs has its own balcony. Fenced dog yard, roomy turn out for the horses with storage for tack and feed - surrounded by plenty of miles of trails!
